{"type": "article", "id": 26601, "title": "鸭嘴兽茶滤", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151943WGxC8B4FozIHSTbK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gongdreen.com/\">Gongdreen</a> 的设计师们之前就制作过一系列模仿了动物造型的产品，这一次他们参照了或许是这个星球上最奇怪的动物，鸭嘴兽。这款名为 VivaBoo 的茶滤有着非常可爱的外形，使用起来也非常方便：打开它白色的“肚子”，装入茶叶后把它挂在杯沿上就行了。茶滤一共有三种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://gongdreen.com/?product=vivaboo-tea-infuser\">售价为 12 美元</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151940i4j8bGgz5XNZAKhr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519409PI3yuEkF2gOJzDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519405bfcZV8viRHM7t9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151941CfwglRyVkEp0A1aG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}